data.name: Label18.Text
data.value:
If you want to find the value of Tn then type ? inside Tn and fill all the other with Numerical Values. Similary if you want to find a or d or n, Use the above method but type ? inside the term you want to find.
Example: If you want to find a(first term) with values Tn = 4 d = 2 n = 2 then enter the values in this form 4 = ? +( 2 - 1 ) 2
